单及商誉损失高达上亿元。特斯拉表示将上诉。据此前报道，被告西安李女士 2021 年 3 月驾驶特斯拉发生交通事故。2021 年 4 月 19 日，西安李女士和河南张女士，身着带有「刹车失灵」字样服装，出现在上海车展特斯拉展台。当天，河南张女士因扰乱公共秩序被公安机关行政拘留，西安李女士被处以行政警告。(中国新闻周刊) 中新经纬 - 快报 - 特斯拉要求刹车失灵事件女车主赔偿 500 万"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-9cdabd09bf202c1395b7f1c7bb5d6ac3_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632096669"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIubzphK+mico2EAMaCTEwMjc0NDY4NiCF85CrBjAAOPsCQBVyCTYzMjA5NjY2OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1701136291.950043", "card_id": "Q_346249699", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1074}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有没有一个演好人一身正气，演坏人又让人恨得牙痒痒的那种演员？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有没有这种演技的演员，我想看他所有电影"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c8775690cf5c951315894c5df34ac5de_hd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/346249699"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IubzphK+mico2EAMaCDM5MjIyMDU1IKih/OsFMAA4kRhAFnIJMzQ2MjQ5Njk5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1701136291.950488", "card_id": "Q_632121026", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待一加总裁说一加 12 产品力超越所有骁龙 8gen3 手机的 Pro 版，产品力强悍还是吹嘘？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一加总裁李杰 Louis 发文，一加 12 的产品力要超越所有骁龙 8gen3 手机的 Pro 版。vivo x100pro 、小米 14pro 、 iQoo12pro，一加 12 在产品力上是否真正超越他们？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7ce5854d881e27656e4d864a14302024_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_colo